---
title: Chermoula Lamb & Cheesy Greens Gozleme with Cherry Tomato Couscous Salad & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Gözleme is a street food favourite, featuring thin, crispy flatbread stuffed with delicious filling. Let’s put a spin on the classic Turkish flatbread with a bold, aromatic filling of tender chermoula-spiced lamb and cheesy greens. This cuisine combo gets five stars!
